Hey Guys, My name is Jesse and I started renting from Turo a couple years ago. I have always had great experiences and being a car enthusiast I started renting out my personal cars. I treat every car I drive like it was my personal car and I hope for the same when I rent mine out.

My hours are pretty open and 7 days a week but if you need a special accommodation please just message me for pick ups overnight. I will always do my best to accommodate any request.

We are William Rides. We are the largest host on Turo in Chicago with over 50 vehicles for rent. We strive to have the most variety of vehicles from the latest cars to the basic economy car.

We will do our absolute best to always provide a hassle free and smooth transaction when renting vehicles. You can always count on great service and a clean car, at your convenience. Cars are always smoke and pet free.

I strive to give you a 5 star experience! Expect your car to be clean and with a full tank of gas. Pickup and dropoff will be super simple and it all will be coordinated by me saving you time and give you a stress free experience. All you'll need to do is enjoy your trip! I use Turo to make a little extra cash for me and my son to travel more. He loves going on road trips with me. I plan on adding more cars in the future so think of me when you need a car to get around.
